#

Classic Beet Borscht

75 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetarianlow-fat

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

main

Tags:

soupcomfort foodhearty

Description

A vibrant and hearty soup made with beets and served hot, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 4 medium
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • carrots: 2 medium, diced
  • onion: 1 large, chopped
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • sour cream: for serving
  • fresh dill: for garnish
